## <a id="prerequisites"></a>Prerequisites

To complete installation of Altoros Log Search for VMware Tanzu, you need the following:

* CPU, RAM, and disk resources for 11 VMs for shared service plan
* CPU, RAM, and disk resources for 12 VMs for on-demand service plan
* Internet connectivity between the networks where the VMware Tanzu deployment and Log Search are installed. Altoros recommends installing Log Search on the same network with VMware Tanzu.

## <a id="requirements"></a>Requirements

Altoros Log Search for VMware Tanzu has the following requirements:

* [Tanzu Application Services](https://network.pivotal.io/products/elastic-runtime) v2.5.x, v2.6.x, v2.7.x, v2.8.x, v2.9.x
